Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:14.68,ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}感情の名前なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.13,0:22:18.69,ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}言い出せばキリがないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.91,0:22:22.30,ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}君の目が叫ぶのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:26.36,ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}本能で聞き分ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:26.95,ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Trust
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:28.21,ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}付き纏う
